#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start to &kgeography;"
msgstr "&kgeography; kiirtutvustus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you run &kgeography; for the first time, it first asks you to choose a "
"map to start with."
msgstr ""
"Kui käivitad &kgeography; esimest korda, palutakse sul valida mõne riigi "
"kaart."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can filter the map list using <guilabel>Filter Maps</guilabel> text "
"field. Just enter a few first letters of the map name to narrow down the "
"list to a few matches."
msgstr ""
"Kaartide loendit saab filtreerida tekstivälja <guilabel>Kaartide "
"filtreerimine</guilabel> abil. Kirjuta lihtsalt paar kaardi nime algustähte "
"kasti, millega juba piiratakse tunduvalt nimekirja."

